	<h1> Goat Cheese/Beetroot Salad </h1>
	<img src="Goat CheeseBeetroot Salad.jpg" alt="Goat Cheese Beetroot Salad">
	<h2> Ingredients </h2>
<ul>
	<li> <p>Lettuce/ Any leafy salad base you like </p> </li>
	<li> <p>Beetroot (cut into slices)/p> </li>
	<li> <p>Goats Cheese (cut into slices)</p> </li>
	<li> <p>Walnuts (Crush up a bit) </p> </li>
	<li> <p>Balsamic Dressing (you can also make your own if you know how lol) </p> </li>
</ul>
	<h2> Method </h2>
<ol>
	<li> <p> Put lettuce/ leafy salad on a plate</p> </li>
	<li> <p>Add beetroot and goats cheese on the top</p> </li>
	<li> <p>Sprinkle crushed walnuts on top </p> </li>
	<li> <p>Drizzle balsamic dressing over </p> </li>
</ol>
  </body>
